##Notes for Week 6: 2.3 The Profit Maximizing Rule

# Marginal Revenue
*Marginal Revenue* is the change in total revenue from an additional unit sold.

*Average Revenue* is the total revenue divided by the quantity sold.

*Change in Profit* is the difference between Marginal Revenue minus Marginal Cost

